
"---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Insert Mode Mappings

" move line up and down >>> Alt + k/j
inoremap <A-k> <Esc>:m-2<CR>
inoremap <A-j> <Esc>:m+<CR>

" move line up and down >>> Alt + up/down
inoremap <A-Up> <Esc>:m-2<CR>
inoremap <A-Down> <Esc>:m+<CR>

